{"tid":323501,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃日本區附加賽名額決定賽－堀北真希vs平井桃@TWICE","createTime":"2017-07-15T15:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T14:00:20.000Z","uid":92376,"like":63,"dislike":153,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"743785df3856d4371ef8c058281aa6196025731d","tid":323501,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃日本區附加賽名額決定賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-7-16 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uwEGvAA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuwEGvAA.png&h=c7c803a4&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/aoVAjQe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaoVAjQe.png&h=298f7f90&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(演員)　(歌手)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">堀北真希 vs 平井桃@TWICE</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">賽事時限為22小時，會員可於本帖發起後22小時內於以正負評方式(前者正評;後者負評)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"7a02eef806efee511817e2e54e81477eb47b1d8e","tid":323501,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"其實投票，唔一定每種投票既性質都係要大家識或者鍾意果一個人先至可以投票<br />\n大家可以憑住審美眼光黎投票，決定邊個好啲靚啲咪投邊個，選美評審都唔會知道面前既女仔係咩人，只係客觀選擇<br />\n巴打們不妨可以抱住呢個心態黎參與我地既活動呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW呢場勝出者將會喺月尾兩回合附加賽對韓國既宋智孝,請注意"},{"pid":"c456b8c944d49262f5f7d780a932320ef613cc2a","tid":323501,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:05:12.000Z","msg":"原本今日應該係有村架純,點知臨完提名先比maki反cup<br />\n慘慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c30741a41c2e8fca2141ca56920f4e1da9645b","tid":323501,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"有一個對堀北真希唔係咁利好既因素係佢已經息左影<br />\n但係仲佔左一個組別附加賽名額<br />\n會唔會因為而引起部分人不滿而令選票流向對家呢,我地繼續跟進呢場決定日本附加賽席位代表既重要賽事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ed38c839223eb2d5054dd1602b71c01ef150e8","tid":323501,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a46a43f19a253cf7f1da3091fd43b828aa05c28","tid":323501,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ceba84b517f97fa93e6d54fe76ecbe18c3c5de5","tid":323501,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046d0a67b9208531d4ef53b5336ab354e183232a","tid":323501,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043885991f283b6efb37a6f4d9d424dc4a7b6988","tid":323501,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b7b01346f0062